{"id":24721,"date":"2024-01-29T17:18:27","date_gmt":"2023-08-29T17:18:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=24721"},"modified":"2024-04-15T10:55:59","modified_gmt":"2024-04-15T05:25:59","slug":"foyer-lighting-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/foyer-lighting-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"9 Stylish Foyer Lighting Ideas For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>9 lighting ideas for creating a lit entrance to your home!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lights are such a vital part of home interior design that they can make or break the appearance and functionality of a space. Interior designers will always tell you to invest in good lighting for your home. Why? Because a great deal of thought goes into the design considering the availability or lack of natural lighting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Foyers or entrances to your homes in modern apartments are seldom naturally well-lit spaces. When your home has a pretty entrance, it also needs stunning lighting that is equally practical. Here are nine styles for foyer lighting ideas for your home that we like.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hanging Lights Top Our List Of Foyer Lighting Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This small and cosy entryway has a beautiful and functional design, which serves many purposes. It encompasses a shoe rack, small storage, coat hanger and a small seating arrangement. The exposed hanging bulbs used for foyer lighting here nicely reflect light off the light colours used in the design and the mirror and ensure that the place is adequately lit.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29163403\/hanging-lights-top-our-list-of-foyer-lighting-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Foyer lighting ideas with hanging lights, shoe rack, small storage and small seating arrangement\" class=\"wp-image-24722\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29163403\/hanging-lights-top-our-list-of-foyer-lighting-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29163403\/hanging-lights-top-our-list-of-foyer-lighting-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29163403\/hanging-lights-top-our-list-of-foyer-lighting-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29163403\/hanging-lights-top-our-list-of-foyer-lighting-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Hang exposed bulbs for minimal and functional foyer lighting<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Combination Of Hanging Lights And Spotlights Works Great For The Entranceway<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>These tiny spotlights are extremely helpful in illuminating selected spots in a space like the foyer. Coupled with the hanging pendant lights, the bright white of the furniture and the mirrors, these ensure that the small square entrance to your home is warm and welcoming.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164154\/foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-with-a-combination-of-hanging-lights-and-spotlights-works-great-for-the-entranceway.jpg\" alt=\"Foyer lighting ideas pictures with a combination of hanging lights and spotlights works great for the entranceway\" class=\"wp-image-24723\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164154\/foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-with-a-combination-of-hanging-lights-and-spotlights-works-great-for-the-entranceway.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164154\/foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-with-a-combination-of-hanging-lights-and-spotlights-works-great-for-the-entranceway-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164154\/foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-with-a-combination-of-hanging-lights-and-spotlights-works-great-for-the-entranceway-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164154\/foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-with-a-combination-of-hanging-lights-and-spotlights-works-great-for-the-entranceway-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Use a combination of ceiling and hanging lights for proper illumination of the foyer<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Light Panels In A False Ceiling Help Light Up A Larger Area<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If your entranceway is as spacious as this foyer, you can go for similar panel lighting options. Panels keep the lights from becoming too bright and harsh and also add another dimension to the design.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164431\/entrance-foyer-lighting-ideas-for-light-panels-in-a-false-ceiling-help-light-up-a-larger-area.jpg\" alt=\"Entrance foyer lighting ideas on light panels in a false ceiling help light up a larger area\" class=\"wp-image-24724\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164431\/entrance-foyer-lighting-ideas-for-light-panels-in-a-false-ceiling-help-light-up-a-larger-area.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164431\/entrance-foyer-lighting-ideas-for-light-panels-in-a-false-ceiling-help-light-up-a-larger-area-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164431\/entrance-foyer-lighting-ideas-for-light-panels-in-a-false-ceiling-help-light-up-a-larger-area-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164431\/entrance-foyer-lighting-ideas-for-light-panels-in-a-false-ceiling-help-light-up-a-larger-area-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Panel lights with design detailing look stunning for the foyer<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bohemian Foyer Lighting Pairs Well With Wooden Furniture<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The wooden partition to this living room creates an exciting facade between the entrance and the hall. This relatively spacious foyer needs plenty of lighting. While the spotlights help illuminate the brown wooden finishes, the bohemian hanging light helps spot-lighting the storage and seating arrangement.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164633\/foyer-ceiling-light-ideas-for-bohemian-foyer-lighting-pairs-well-with-wooden-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"Foyer ceiling light ideas for bohemian foyer lighting pairs well with wooden furniture\" class=\"wp-image-24725\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164633\/foyer-ceiling-light-ideas-for-bohemian-foyer-lighting-pairs-well-with-wooden-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164633\/foyer-ceiling-light-ideas-for-bohemian-foyer-lighting-pairs-well-with-wooden-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164633\/foyer-ceiling-light-ideas-for-bohemian-foyer-lighting-pairs-well-with-wooden-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164633\/foyer-ceiling-light-ideas-for-bohemian-foyer-lighting-pairs-well-with-wooden-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Boho lights make for chic foyer lighting ideas<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Stick To The Basics With Classy Pendant Lights For The Foyer<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A gorgeous foyer is part design and part lighting. This lovely entrance to a modern apartment has a \u2019gram-worthy foyer. Classy pendant lights help keep the space stylish and functional.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164846\/small-foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-where-you-stick-to-the-basics-with-classy-pendant-lights.jpg\" alt=\"Small foyer lighting ideas pictures where you stick to the basics with classy pendant lights\" class=\"wp-image-24726\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164846\/small-foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-where-you-stick-to-the-basics-with-classy-pendant-lights.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164846\/small-foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-where-you-stick-to-the-basics-with-classy-pendant-lights-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164846\/small-foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-where-you-stick-to-the-basics-with-classy-pendant-lights-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29164846\/small-foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-where-you-stick-to-the-basics-with-classy-pendant-lights-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">You can\u2019t go wrong with pendant lights for the foyer<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Personalise your home office setup for maximum efficiency!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/14223911\/personalise-your-home-office-setup-for-maximum-efficiency.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vintage Lighting For The Foyer Has Its Own Charm<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This rather spacious apartment entrance has a stunning mirror to create an illusion of even more space. The mirror also reflects all the natural and artificial light in this area. It works as an aide to the single vintage foyer ceiling light and helps illuminate the entire space efficiently.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29165021\/vintage-foyer-lighting-ideas-has-its-own-charm.jpg\" alt=\"Vintage foyer lighting ideas has its own charm for the lamps for the lobby\" class=\"wp-image-24727\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29165021\/vintage-foyer-lighting-ideas-has-its-own-charm.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29165021\/vintage-foyer-lighting-ideas-has-its-own-charm-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29165021\/vintage-foyer-lighting-ideas-has-its-own-charm-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29165021\/vintage-foyer-lighting-ideas-has-its-own-charm-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Go old school with vintage style lamps for the lobby<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Chandeliers In Foyer Lighting Ideas Have Our Heart<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This chic-looking foyer has multiple types of lights to ensure that the space is brightly lit. The false ceiling has concealed LED light strips that bounce off the ceiling to provide a subtle light. The spotlights help focus on the seating area. The chandelier light has to be the centrepiece in the scheme of things here. It elegantly lights up the lobby and adds an element of beauty to the design.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29165228\/modern-chandeliers-in-foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-have-our-heart.jpg\" alt=\"Modern chandeliers in foyer lighting ideas pictures have our heart\" class=\"wp-image-24728\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29165228\/modern-chandeliers-in-foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-have-our-heart.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29165228\/modern-chandeliers-in-foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-have-our-heart-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29165228\/modern-chandeliers-in-foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-have-our-heart-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29165228\/modern-chandeliers-in-foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-have-our-heart-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A combination of multiple lights individually serve the common purpose of lighting up the entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Wall Lamps Can Do Wonders For Foyer Lighting<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We cannot stop admiring this tastefully designed foyer! The design has a classy, artistic touch to it, and the same is reflected in the choice of lighting for this foyer. This space has a window to bring in natural light. Hence the artificial lighting required is minimal. The classy wall lamp lights up the seating space in a stylish manner.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29170431\/foyer-lighting-ideas-where-modern-wall-lamps-can-do-wonders.jpg\" alt=\"Foyer lighting ideas where modern wall lamps can do wonders\" class=\"wp-image-24729\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29170431\/foyer-lighting-ideas-where-modern-wall-lamps-can-do-wonders.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29170431\/foyer-lighting-ideas-where-modern-wall-lamps-can-do-wonders-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29170431\/foyer-lighting-ideas-where-modern-wall-lamps-can-do-wonders-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29170431\/foyer-lighting-ideas-where-modern-wall-lamps-can-do-wonders-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Wall lamps are the apt choice for foyer lighting when there is a natural light source for the foyer <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Table Lamps Can Be An Interesting Choice For Foyer Lighting<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Table lamps can be slightly restricted in terms of the area they cover, but they look and work great when backed up by another light source. This rather spacious lobby in a pastel and white colour palette looks fresh and inviting. The spotlight helps light up the area around the door, while the table lamp covers the storage and seating section.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29170635\/foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-where-table-lamps-can-be-an-interesting-choice.jpg\" alt=\"Foyer lighting ideas pictures where table lamps can be an interesting choice\" class=\"wp-image-24730\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29170635\/foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-where-table-lamps-can-be-an-interesting-choice.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29170635\/foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-where-table-lamps-can-be-an-interesting-choice-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29170635\/foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-where-table-lamps-can-be-an-interesting-choice-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/29170635\/foyer-lighting-ideas-pictures-where-table-lamps-can-be-an-interesting-choice-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Bring out vintage table lamps to light up your foyer\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A well-designed foyer deserves its spot in the sun, well, in this case, proper lighting. The primary rule to remember while selecting the right lights for your home entrance is that they should necessarily be equally practical as they are beautiful.<br>If you are exploring options to make your foyer designs functional, you can also read <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/how-to-design-a-foyer\/\">Ideas On How To Design A Foyer<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n      